node.text:
This is the story of the Alta Environmental Center. 🌱
 
The year-round efforts of the Alta Environmental Center (AEC – @altaenvironment) come to life in the latest video exploration with Sweetgrass Productions. The AEC’s dedication to sustainability and Alta’s land conservation efforts are central to our 83-year-old ski area ethos. We care deeply for this land that provides us deep powder turns and solace from the fast-paced daily world. We know that powder turns and conservation go hand in hand.
 
This is our story of sustainability.
(Link In Bio) 

🎥: @sweetgrassp 
#AltaEnvironment #Sustainability #Conservation #Stewardship

Thanks to all of you who have joined us this summer for a stewardship event.

node.text:
You can pick your friends and you can pick your nose, but you can’t pick the wildflowers. 🌻

We are seeing increased impacts from off-trail use and the trampling and picking of wildflowers in the Albion Basin.
⁣
We all love to admire and share the beauty of the wildflowers in the Albion Basin, but please stay on trail and leave the wildflowers for the bees.
⁣
It is everyone’s responsibility to conserve the environment and be good stewards of the land. Working together, we can protect this area for ourselves and future visitors. 

📸: @rockomenzyk 
#recreateresponsibly #dontpickwildflowers #leavenotrace
